					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I came up with a math equation to eject objects straight vertically and horizontally so that the physics work the same both ways.<br /><br />X = Ax + By<br />Y = Cx + Dy<br /><br />popping y:<br />(Y - Cx)/D = y<br /><br />popping x:<br />(X - By)/A = x<br /><br />I haven't figured out how to do slopes while rotated though.</div>

